The '''2014 [[Copa Federacion Venezolana de Ciclismo]]''' was a one-day women's cycle race held in [[Venezuela]] beginning and finishing in [[San Felipe, Yaracuy|San Felipe]]<ref>http://www.procyclingstats.com/race/Copa_Federacion_Venezolana_de_Ciclismo_2014</ref> on 17 May [[2014 in women's road cycling|2014]]. The race had a [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] rating of [[UCI category|1.2]].
