{{Infobox model | name = Helen Svedin | image = | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1976|10|22|df=yes}} | birth_place = [[Sollefteå]], [[Sweden]] | death_date = | death_place = | height = {{height|m=1.76}} | haircolor = Blonde | eyecolor = Blue | agency = [[Elite Model Management]] – [[New York City]], SS&M Model Management, [[Munich Models]], Wiener Models, Modelwerk, East West Models | spouse = [[Luís Figo]] | website = }}
'''Helen Svedin''' (born 22 October 1976) is a Swedish [[Model (person)|model]] and the wife of Portuguese footballer [[Luís Figo]].
The face of [[H&M]],<ref>Aizlewood, John. [http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/article671455.ece "The top 10 World Cup wives."] ''[[The Times]]'', June 4, 2006.</ref> Svedin is married to former Portuguese footballer [[Luís Figo]]. They met in 1996 at a [[Joaquín Cortés]] show in [[Barcelona]].<ref>Sanchidrian, Antonio. [http://www.elmundo.es/papel/2006/09/20/madrid/2026792.html "Helen Swedin añora España."] ''[[El Mundo (Spain)|El Mundo]]'', September 20, 2006.</ref> They have three children together: Daniela (born 1999), Martina (born 2002) and Stella (born 2004). They presently live in [[Madrid]], [[Spain]].
Svedin has been in advertisements of Ana Sousa, Arena, Don Algodón, Friday's Project, [[Giorgio Armani]], [[Guess?]], Isdin, [[Kia Motors]], [[Land Rover]], [[L'Oréal]], Luciano Padovan, [[Nike, Inc.|Nike]], [[Vista Alegre (company)|Vista Alegre]], and [[Henkel#Brands|Schwarzkopf]]. She has appeared on the covers of ''[[GQ]]'', ''[[Elle (magazine)|Elle]]'', ''Telva'', ''[[Marie Claire]]'', and ''Woman''.<ref>{{cite web |url= http://playerwags.com/luis-figos-wife-helen-svedin/ |title= Luis Figo’s Wife Helen Svedin |author= monahesah |date= 22 Nov 2014 |website= Player Wags |access-date= 23 May 2015}}</ref>
